Multiple types of things can be achieved using Amazon Rekognition
-> Object and Scene Detection
Automatically Labels Objects, Concepts and Scences in your images (with confidence score)

-> Image Moderation
Detects explicit or suggestive adult content in your images (with confidence score)

-> Facial Analysis
Get complete analysis of facial attributes (with confidence scores)

-> Celebrity Recognition
Automatically recognizes celebrities in images (with confidence scores)

-> Face Comparision
Compare faces to see how closely they match based on similarity percentage

-> Text in Image
Detects and extracts text in your image

-> Video Analysis
Service analyzes video and detects objects, activities, people, celebrities, and more in video and live streams

Properties
Can Integrate into Powerful Visual Analysis
Continuously Learning
Integrated with AWS Services


